<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-03-06T13:46:36-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-03-06T13:46:36-05:00</published><updated> 2024-03-06T13:46:36-05:00</updated><title> Meta 解释 WhatsApp 的加密聊天如何与第三方服务配合使用</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;以黑色显示 WhatsApp 徽标的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/i1BUh_75x04PLRJzw767EBDx_iI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73186810/STK110_whats_app_Kradtke_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;yduPTC&quot;>;现在欧盟针对数字“看门人”的新规则” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24091592/eu-dma-competition-compliance-deadline-big-tech-policy-changes&quot;>;已上线&lt;/a>;， Meta 已准备好告诉大家 &lt;a href=&quot;https://engineering.fb.com/2024/03/06/security/whatsapp-messenger-messaging-interoperability-eu/&quot;>;WhatsApp 和 Messenger 将如何提供端到端服务- 端加密&lt;/a>; (E2EE)，同时遵守&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24040543/eu-dma-digital-markets-act-big-tech-antitrust&quot;>;数字市场Act&lt;/a>; 的 (DMA) 第三方聊天要求。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;vyFovg&quot;>;DMA 要求 Meta“必须在收到请求后三个月内做好与其他服务的互操作性准备”，但根据博客文章，实际上将其开放供公众使用可能需要更长的时间。这些要求还仅要求在新法规的“第一年”支持一对一聊天和共享图像、视频或语音消息等文件，然后随着时间的推移扩展到包括群聊和通话。&lt;/p>; &lt; div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;yCWE37&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[ {“title”：“欧盟新的竞争规则即将生效 - 以下是科技巨头的应对方式”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24091592/eu-dma-竞争合规性截止日期大科技政策变更&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;eU59Jr&quot;>;Meta 表示第三方提供商必须.. .&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24092384/meta-third-party-encrypted-chats-implementation-eu-dma&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24092384/meta-third-party-encrypted-chats-implementation-eu-dma" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24092384/meta-third-party-encrypted-chats-implementation-eu-dma</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-06T13:24:12-05:00</published><updated> 2024-03-06T13:24:12-05:00</updated><title> M2 MacBook Air 已经以比新起售价低 100 美元的价格出售</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;M2 MacBook Air。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-DDnPXqmI2vgs8L9mciWHqbON7A=/0x0:1440x960/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73186751/macbookairm2.0.jpg&quot;/ >; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;M2 MacBook Air 的价格低于 1,000 美元，仍然具有很高的价值。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;oRh8fH&quot;>;随着 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/4/24089999 的推出/apple-macbook-air-m3-announced-13-15-inch&quot;>;M3 MacBook Air&lt;/a>;，苹果终于逐步淘汰老化的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21569603/ apple-macbook-air-m1-review-price-specs-features-arm-silicon&quot;>;M1 型号&lt;/a>;。从价值的角度来看，后者可以说是苹果过去几年中最好的产品，而现在，M2 MacBook Air 似乎准备好继续前进。我们已经看到 B&amp;H Photo 等零售商提供 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com% 2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1710301-REG%2Fapple_mlxy3ll_a_13_6_macbook_air_m2.html%2F&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F3%2F6%2F24092128%2Fapple-m2-macbook-air - ring-stick-up-cam-prince-of-persia-lost-crown-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;我们在 13 英寸基本型号上看到的最优惠价格&lt;/ a>; 配备 8GB RAM、256GB 存储和八核 M2。价格降至 899 美元，比原来的建议零售价低 200 美元，比新的 999 美元起价便宜 100 美元。您还可以&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fpr